Here are the current steps to take to build percolator:

1) Build Xerces
./configure --disable-network
make

2) Load xsd module
module load xsd

3) Update cmake/FindXSD.cmake with path to binary and include files, ex.

XSD_INCLUDE_DIR
/net/gs/vol3/software/modules-sw/xsd/3.3.0/Linux/RHEL5/x86_64/libxsd
XSD_EXECUTABLE
/net/gs/vol3/software/modules-sw/xsd/3.3.0/Linux/RHEL5/x86_64/bin/


4) Load Boost module

5) Edit percolator/src/CMakeLists.txt
   Update CMAKE_INCLUDE_PATHs with directory to boost directory before find_package(Boost ...), ex.
   SET(CMAKE_INCLUDE_PATH "/net/gs/vol3/software/modules-sw/boost/1.45.0/Linux/RHEL5/x86_64/include" ${CMAKE_INCLUDE_PATH})
SET(CMAKE_LIBRARY_PATH "/net/gs/vol3/software/modules-sw/boost/1.45.0/Linux/RHEL5/x86_64/lib" ${CMAKE_LIBRARY_PATH})

find_package(Boost COMPONENTS filesystem system REQUIRED)

6) cmake .
7) make
8) YAY!
   

